c: 5
v: 94
t: Aey eman walo! Allah Taalaa qadray shikar say tumhara imtehan keray ga jin tak tumharay haath aur tumharay naizay phonch saken gay takay Allah Taalaa maloom ker ley kay kaun shaks iss say binn dekhay darta hai so jo shaks iss kay baad hadd say niklay ga uss kay wastay dard naak saza hai